==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hornbug
<hw>Horn"bug`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
large nocturnal beetle of the genus <gen>Lucanus</gen> (as <spn>Lucanus
capreolus</spn>, and <spn>Lucanus dama</spn>), having long, curved upper
jaws, resembling a sickle. The grubs are found in the trunks of old
trees.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Horned</ent>⟦br⟧
